{"tid":948801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說今日公司抽禮物 點做先啱...?","createTime":"2018-12-20T10:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T14:57:24.000Z","uid":164163,"like":13,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49537eb2ada80bb264e9b683474abfc8e01f6632","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"小弟係做物流運輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話說今日公司交換禮物 咁大家都知有女人呢種生物存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一定有是非㗎啦 咁所有同事(包括我)都好憎一個同事 因為呢個同事因為同人講嘢啲語氣真係好撩交打 但係因為今日呢個同事請事假(好似話參加婚禮) 所以就無返 不過佢前幾日已經交低咗份禮物 所以佢都可以有份抽(雖然佢無返)<br />\n<br />\n因為我下星期二喺另外一間分店返工 會撞到呢個同事 所以我腦細就叫我下星期二將份禮物俾返呢個同事 正當大家抽完準備散band嗰陣 啲女同事就行過嚟問我 &quot;喂 Maria抽到嗰份禮物係咩嚟㗎?&quot; 咁我就show俾佢哋睇 之後有個女仔就話攞佢嗰份同我交換啊 反正佢無返都唔知㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最後話趕住返屋企湊仔 所以聽日見面再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好鬼憎抽禮物 一定會有呢啲咁仆街嘅事情發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你哋遇到呢個情況 你哋會點做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 梗係跟大圍啦 唔通想做下一個犯眾憎咩?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 堅決說不 有啲正義感<br />\n<br />\n利申: 抽到個溫度計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   你老母家陣做診所姑娘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  俾我知道係邊條仆街買 我實斬佢7749份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6860c0e7b6a72bb6211a2bfa18ae8654e49d9e","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43a028a2b8e4f4f4db18e4f45d88f04eee676d83","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3dfe08c2e6b74360549e2f0a5601924eae4dd235","tid":948801,"uid":14737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"跟大圍, 同佢講maria抽到溫度計"},{"pid":"10d1f0eba4795fabdf1e0506956bbcb68904e7db","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3dfe08c2e6b74360549e2f0a5601924eae4dd235","tid":948801,"uid":14737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"跟大圍, 同佢講maria抽到溫度計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"同邊個佢講?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382597836318498644de28737e11790039d4d7eb","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"212b143deb395faf4b451960fae0c16c8f3fffc2","tid":948801,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"是但啦，咁認真做乜"},{"pid":"a5ece7df3f8a81b49df4fda1ec0956ca3474f467","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"212b143deb395faf4b451960fae0c16c8f3fffc2","tid":948801,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"是但啦，咁認真做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"兩邊都無所謂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6839cb947b340be67ed482036c3c0b1f3a63fcad","tid":948801,"uid":46347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"212b143deb395faf4b451960fae0c16c8f3fffc2","tid":948801,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"是但啦，咁認真做乜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"最婆媽嗰個係樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d82696abe63f56fc5397293a2d90bd05cabe4ed","tid":948801,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6839cb947b340be67ed482036c3c0b1f3a63fcad","tid":948801,"uid":46347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"212b143deb395faf4b451960fae